data.description: Welcome Home to 19016 Turkey Egg Road! If you are looking for quiet and peaceful living, you need to see this! 4 bedrooms, 2  full bathrooms, sunken family room, and naturally lit sunroom. Venture outside to unwind on the deck during the day or gather under the deck lights at night. Escape to the fish pond and watch the sunset. Don’t worry, this home is well lit at night with dusk to dawn lights around the perimeter. BUT WAIT !!! Did I mention the 3 car, 2 bay garage!! Make this an extra living space, workshop, or house your cars here! The choice is yours! Feel right at home here! Also close to major highways. (85), near major distribution centers (Walmart, Aldi, Amazon), Dinwiddie and Southside elementary, Dinwiddie middle school, Dinwiddie high school, and Dinwiddie courthouse! Less than 30 min to Ft. Gregg-Adams (Formally Ft. Lee) and less than 40 min from Ft. Barefoot (formally Ft. Pickett). 5 min from closest fire department, sheriff’s department, EMT, medical center, and post office.  It doesn’t get much better than this!   This area is also Eligible for USDA loan = 0% down payment !!! Come and See for yourself!
